            <h1>About Us</h1>
            <p>Proengineers Learning & Research Center is a one-stop destination for comprehensive technical education,
                practical training, and industry-aligned skill development. We empower students from Diploma, Degree,
                BE/BTech, BSc IT, BCA, and other technical backgrounds to become future-ready professionals.</p>
            <p>Our programs span across various engineering disciplines including:</p>
            <ul>
                <li>Computer Engineering</li>
                <li>Mechanical Engineering</li>
                <li>Civil Engineering</li>
                <li>Electronics Engineering</li>
                <li>Electrical Engineering</li>
                <li>Artificial Intelligence & Machine Learning (AI/ML)</li>
                <li>Mechatronics</li>
            </ul>
            <p>We also provide hands-on apprenticeship opportunities in specialized trades like Electrical Wiring, CNC
                Machine Operation, and more—bridging the gap between classroom knowledge and on-ground industrial
                practice.</p>
            <p>With a team of seasoned professionals and strong industry collaborations, we aim to build a workforce
                that’s both technically sound and practically skilled.</p>
        </div>
    </section>

