                <li><strong>Mechanical & Mechatronics:</strong> 3D Printing, SolidWorks, CNC, Robotics</li>
                <li><strong>Civil:</strong> AutoCAD, STAAD Pro, Construction Materials Testing</li>
                <li><strong>Electronics & Electrical:</strong> PCB Designing, PLC & SCADA, IoT with Arduino/Raspberry Pi
                </li>
                <li><strong>Multidisciplinary:</strong> Industry 4.0, Smart Automation, Renewable Energy Systems</li>
